SHAPEFILE_2_DEF Mammifères   shapefile_type               shapefile_first_feature   shape_dimension              AUTO   biogeograp                   varchar(200)   chao2_esti                   number(20,10)   expected_s                   number(20,10)   completene                   number(20,10)   maille10                     varchar(200)   mean_expec                   number(20,10)   occurrence                   number(20,10)   percentage                   number(20,10)   total_spec                   number(20,10)   species_co                   number(20,10)   geom_wkt                     varchar(200)   ignorancei                   number(20,10)   si                           number(20,10)   knowledges                   double
